# No Debug Build

**Always use release builds for veracity binaries.**

- **DO**: `cargo build --release` or `cargo build --release --bin <name>`
- **DO NOT**: `cargo build` (debug) or `./target/debug/veracity-*`

Release binaries live in `target/release/`. Use them for running veracity tools.
